# Caddy TLS reverse proxy in front of boringd (public endpoint).
# sslip.io resolves 162-43-188-89.sslip.io -> the box IP, so Caddy gets a real
# Let's Encrypt cert and terminates HTTPS/WSS. boringd binds 127.0.0.1:8080
# (BORING_ADDR) so it is only reachable through this proxy.
#
# Swap the hostname for your own domain once DNS points at the box.
162-43-188-89.sslip.io {
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:8080
}
